title: Boat rentals
description:
Row, paddle or yacht motorboat. With us, you choose how to get along the archipelago's copper and cutters. With our boats it is possible for you to get the Roslagen really close. Look out over the archipelago from our beautiful island or rent a boat and you will also feel the breeze of Roslagens archipelago.

Groups

One tip is to challenge the experience and try our boat orientation with your friends. Divided into teams from each boat you are looking for exposed bojys via a chart. At each bucket there is a clue, so keep the correct course and look for the solution, then you win.
